# UI and design system

## Tokens and theme

- Use **semantic Tailwind tokens**: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, `bg-card`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-primary`, `text-primary-foreground`, `ring-ring`, etc. Avoid raw hex in components unless defining a one-off gradient/beam (landing-style accents).
- **Brand accent**: green primary (`--primary` light/dark in `app/globals.css`). Keep dashboards restrained; marketing pages may use stronger gradients (e.g. emerald → teal) but should still compose with CSS variables where possible.
- **Dark mode**: `class` strategy via `next-themes`; use `dark:` variants. Custom variant is set in globals (`@custom-variant dark`).

## Components

- Build from **`@/components/ui/*`** (Button, Card, Input, Tabs, etc.) with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes.
- **Forms**: `react-hook-form` + `zod` + `@hookform/resolvers` when adding real forms; mirror existing patterns in the repo.
- **Icons**: `lucide-react` only; default icon sizing matches shadcn patterns (`size-4` inline with buttons unless overridden).
- **Animation**: `motion/react` (Motion) for landing and expressive UI; keep motion subtle on dense dashboards unless matching an existing pattern.

## Investor dashboard density

- Routes under `app/investor/**` should stay **compact** vs default shadcn spacing.
- Import `investorDensity` and `investorCardClass` from `@/components/investor/investor-density` for page layout, grids, and Card overrides instead of inventing new density scales.

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD — consistent investor shells
import { investorDensity, investorCardClass } from '@/components/investor/investor-density';

<div className={investorDensity.page}>
  <Card className={investorCardClass()}>...</Card>
</div>
```

## Adding new UI

- New generic primitives → shadcn workflow / `components/ui` (see repo `components.json`).
- New reusable non-primitive pieces → `components/shared` or domain folder, not scattered copies in every page.
